flowRoot.flowPara: URL Power
The most powerful part of Timeomat, however, is it's ability to give easy access to all of the functions via your adress bar.
You want to start a 7 minute timer?
Just type timeomat.com/7min.
You want to start a countdown to christmas?
Type timeomat.com/christmas
You want to start a countdown to the second of may?
Type timeomat.com/2011-05-02
Can you find some more shortcuts? :-)
Timeomat
One of the most common features of cell phones are its time features. Almost every phone has a built in clock, alarm, stopwatch and timer.
But do you know a good website which provides that features? Well, I don't. So I decided to make my own.
Timeomat tries to wrap three principles in one gorgeous website.
1. Keep it simple
2. but yet powerful
3. and equip it with a beautiful design
If you have to keep an eye on the time check out the fancy clock.
Tracking your lap times or measuring the time you need to eat a whole pizza has never been that easy.
Choose between various sounds for the alarm clock. Waking up has never been so pleasant.
Take a 20 minutes nap, start a countdown to christmas or brush your teeth just right.
All with the powerful timer.
